title: Moose rescued after getting trapped under pool cover in New Hampshire backyard - Main Stream Videos
text: Police and firefighters in New Hampshire responded to an unusual call on Thursday morning: a moose stuck in a backyard swimming pool. After the pool cover was removed, the moose casually strolled out of the the pool and headed back into the woods.
